description:
This is a 55 minute workout called 'Standing Pilates Cardio Workout | Burn Fat and Tone Muscles| 30 minutes' from the channel The Girl With The Pilates Mat.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
The workout has a The Groove Session and The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Join me for a 30 minute standing pilates cardio workout. This will raise your heart rate, burn fat, tone muscles and put a smile on your face as we move through low impact, high intensity and fun exercises to boost the metabolism and leave you feeling energised and raring to go. I'll include and warm up and a cool down too. A great session to get going in the morning, I recommend you do this at least three times a week to see and feel the difference in your body. 

Do check out my other high energy workouts here: 

30 Minute Standing Cardio Pilates + Abs https://youtu.be/HauHdwahJvM

15 Minute Standing Pilates for Strong Legs https://youtu.be/gX23jrqY_nk

14 Minute Standing Pilates and Barre Workout: https://youtu.be/PWbRI5PqV2I

Please click the Like button and Subscribe to the channel to help me make more films just for you. 

Stay safe, stay well and enjoy every moment of this day,
Take care, Rachel  x
